Titolo: Harbinger (video game)

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Harbinger is an adventure role-playing video game by American studio Silverback Entertainment published in 2003 by DreamCatcher Interactive. Harbinger takes place on a massive space ship inhabited by multiple warring races and a band of refugees. The player has the choice of three characters with their own unique quests, items, and full-game storylines.